Matter DELIGHT launching party
17.05.20 4pm @ SUBSTANCE rooftop,
녹사평로 46길, 1
🔗 fb.com/events/1771927849485824/
event curated by @caroline_mariet & @paulrsch
.
Matter is honored to invite DJ Bowlcut (KR), in the Line up for this Saturday's celebration.
.
Ju-Hwan You aka DJ Bowlcut borns in S.korea and discovers a joy of music as a turntablist but he extends his taste to LoFi House, Leftfield, Techno and Bass musics. 
DJ Bowlcut is one of a very few DJs who select Leftfield house and techno in seoul. His passion for those genres made him into collects more deep and obscure tracks along with tracks that he made by himself and his work is on Youtube Music channels such as EE.LF, Moskalus and so on.
DJ Bowlcut also running Seoul Community Radio, one of the biggest Underground radio station. and runs ' Hazed & Confucius ' for bringing more audience to Leftfield genres in seoul.
His First EP will release from Honey Badger Records on 2017 May.

学校の授業うけただけの生活で
人並みで終わった学生時代から抜け出したかった。

社会に出たら、やり切ろっうって覚悟したら、

とにかく休まない、

止まらないって感じで続けてるうちに

楽しくて止められない状態。

結果は別として、

伸びる人って自分に負荷をかけ成長し楽しんでいる人。
